 individual cells\nshow remarkable spatial heterogeneity with no two cells exhibiting similar\nbehavior. The prediction that $\\alpha$ should depend on the location of the\ncells in the tumor is amenable to experimental test. The highly heterogeneous\ndynamics of cells in the tumor spheroid provides a plausible mechanism for the\norigin of intratumor heterogeneity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Nov 2019 20:59:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2020 09:46:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-03"}
