ed or eliminated. Finally, we find that the gap edges where the dust\nparticles are accumulated as well as the lopsided large-scale vortices driven\nby a massive planet, if any, are unstable, and they are broken into numerous\nsmall-scale dust-gas vortices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Nov 2019 00:54:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
