ed\ndomains of simulations, and at more extreme values of the governing parameters\nfor thermal forcing and rotation. We also provide experimental evidence for the\nexistence of the sidewall circulation that is in close agreement with the\nsimulation results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Nov 2019 13:14:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2020 09:40:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-12"}
